response.overview: Agent Tony Spears has received intelligence reports of a looming danger at the upcoming climate conference in Cannes France. His superiors have advised him to treat this as a working vacation. He has been booked at the Ritz Carlton Hotel a landmark that receives thousands of visitors each year. It is one of the most photographed hotel in the world. Agent Tony Spears travelled to this destination with his girlfriend Josie Jackson.
response.title: Agent Tony Spears-The Cannes Conundrum 2023
